$TIT_COL
Local Char TITCL(200)(1..3)
Raz TITCL
Case BASPAG
 When "NBSFI"
  TITCL(1) = SI_MES(62)
  TITCL(2) = SI_MES(66)
  TITCL(3) = SI_MES(67)
  If !GORITITCOL
   Titcol [M]NBSFI TITCL(1) For TYP
   Titcol [M]NBSFI TITCL(2) For CODART
   Titcol [M]NBSFI TITCL(3) For SFINUM
  Else
   Titcol [M:SIP3]NBSFI TITCL(1) For TYP
   Titcol [M:SIP3]NBSFI TITCL(2) For CODART
   Titcol [M:SIP3]NBSFI TITCL(3) For SFINUM
  Endif
Endcase
Return

$CHG_STY
Return


